asset.title: See the features of the Access Roll Up Tonneau Cover
asset.description:
Buy Here: http://www.autoanything.com/tonneau-covers/60A1584A0A0.aspx

Access roll up covers feature a "slant back" design that tapers towards the tailgate for a sleek transition. fabrics seals are used and will last the life of the cover. The built-in dual-locking latch automatically locks on both sides and tightens the top when you close the cover. The Access Roll Up Tonneau makes it easy to secure your bed when used in combination with a tailgate lock. The top itself is coated on both sides and remains pliable in extremely cold weather unlike other bed covers. The cover features custom-fit rails, clamps and an adjustable top that requires no tools to tighten. Even the velcro is made to last and is designed to survive 10,000 peels and seals.
